      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"find a new path forward\"... that sounds so easy when you say it. but there is no path. there's just this massive hole where my life used to be. every time i try to think about \"recovering\" or \"starting over\" i just feel physically sick. it feels like the debt and the failure are just who i am now. like, how do you even move past something that defines your entire existence? it just feels like the end of the road.",
