    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"let go of the weight\"... that's what i keep thinking about. just letting go of everything. it feels like the only way to actually stop the noise and the shame is to just... not be here anymore. if i can't fix this, if i can't undo the mess, is there even a point in trying to fight it?",
